# Project Structure

## Overview
The project follows a modular approach with most code residing in the `src` folder. The structure is organized to promote maintainability and clear separation of concerns.

## Root Structure
```sh
src
+-- @types               # Type declarations across the entire application
|
+-- env                  # Type of the env vars
|
+-- lib                  # Re-exporting different libraries preconfigured for the application
|
+-- services             # Feature-oriented integration layer that talks to external/internal APIs using generated clients from `shared/apis`. Responsible for mapping API models to internal DTOs from `shared/dtos` and encapsulating business logic.
|
+-- services/factories   # Factory functions that construct service instances with injected configuration (e.g., `baseURL`, headers, auth).
|
+-- shared               # Source-of-truth shared modules (generated API clients, constants, DTO mappers, validation schemas and errors).
|
+-- trpc                 # tRPC setup, including router composition, procedure definitions, context creation, middlewares, and error handling for the BFF
|
+-- utils                # Shared utility functions
```

## Shared folder structure
```sh
src
|
+-- apis               # Generated TypeScript API clients, operations, and models (e.g., `assets`, `made`) produced by Kubb from Swagger. Do not edit.
|
+-- constants          # Shared constant values used throughout the application
|
+-- dtos               # Mapper classes providing `toDTO` (and optional `toAPI`) to convert between API shapes and internal DTOs consumed by services.
|
+-- validation-schema  # Zod schemas for input validation in tRPC procedures and for guarding service parameters
```

## tRPC folder structure
```sh
src
|
+-- builder               # Generated clients/types from Swagger via Kubb; used by services and tRPC
|
+-- middlewares          # tRPC middlewares (e.g., auth) applied to procedures/routers
|
+-- routes               # Domain routers defining tRPC procedures; validate inputs and call services
|
+-- context.ts           # Creates per-request tRPC context (user/session, services, headers)
|
+-- error-handler.ts     # Centralized tRPC error formatter/handler
|
+-- router.ts            # Composes root app router and exports AppRouter type
```
